Jump Tomorrow;;88;;82;;PG;;When George, a shy and awkward introvert, meets Alicia, a stunning Latin girl, he is instantly smitten. Unfortunately, George is due to marry a childhood friend from Nigeria in just four days' time. When Gerard, a boisterous and lovesick Frenchman stumbles into George's life, the stage is set for a gentle, humorous love story. "Jump Tomorrow" is a road-movie that weaves reality and fantasy into a comic tale of the quirks and passions of modern romance.;;Romance,Comedy;;Joel Hopkins;;2001;;Tunde Adebimpe,Hippolyte Girardot,Natalia Verbeke,James Wilby,Patricia Mauceri,Isiah Whitlock Jr.,Kaili Vernoff,Gene Ruffini,Abiola Abrams;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/jump_tomorrow